==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fanciless
<hw>Fan"ci*less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no fancy;
without ideas or imagination.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A pert or bluff important wight,⟦br⟧
Whose brain is <qex>fanciless</qex>, whose blood is white.</q>
<rj><qau>Armstrong.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fancy</ent>⟦br⟧
